    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it\u2019s looking for a new home. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and road trips. It runs smoothly and still has that great curb appeal! If you're looking for a solid, well-cared-for ride that won't let you down, this is the one. Come check it out and take it for a test drive\u2014I'm sure you'll love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 32500.0,
